shekibobo/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-03-26T03:20:38Z","updated_at":"2013-03-26T03:23:11Z","body":"Sorry, should've been more clear.\n\nGiven two classes:\n\n``` ruby\n# parent.rb\nclass Parent << ActiveRecord::Base\n  has_many :children\nend\n\n# child.rb\nclass Child << ActiveRecord::Base\n  belongs_to :parent\n  attr_accessible :first_name, :last_name, :birthdate\nend\n```\n\nand the AA register:\n\n``` ruby\nActiveAdmin.register Child do\n  belongs_to :parent\n  remove_filter :parent\nend\n```\n\nThe expected behavior is that the index page's sidebar filters for `:first_name`, `:last_name`, and `:birthdate` should all still be present, and only the `:parent` select filter should be removed. Instead the entire select field is missing.\n\nIn fact, calling `remove_filter` on any of the Child model's attributes will remove the entire filter sidebar.\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/activeadmin/activeadmin/issues/comments/15438868/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"shekibobo","id":293858,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5Mzg1OA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/293858?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo","html_url":"https://github.com/shekibobo","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/shekibobo/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com